&lt;l&gt;&lt;del rend="dot"&gt;&lt;gap reason="illegible" unit="character" quantity="1"/&gt;&lt;/del&gt;ūḷar&lt;del rend="dot"&gt;&lt;gap reason="illegible" unit="character" quantity="1"/&gt;&lt;/del&gt;ka pāka tē&lt;lb n="7"/&gt;rē kārkaṇṭu&lt;/l&gt;
&lt;l&gt;pācaṟai nīṭiṉar kāta lōreṉa&lt;/l&gt;
