&lt;l&gt;tōḻi māṟṟalum pulavi tōṟṟaluṅ&lt;/l&gt;
&lt;l&gt;kiḻava&lt;lb n="4"/&gt;ṉ pulattaluṅ kiḻavi pulattalum&lt;/l&gt;
&lt;l&gt;viḻaikunaṉ viḻaiyā ṉivaṉeṉa viḷampalun&lt;/l&gt;
&lt;l&gt;tāykaṇ ṭuraittalun tāṅkiya kā&lt;unclear&gt;ta&lt;/unclear&gt;&lt;lb n="5"/&gt;li&lt;/l&gt;
&lt;l&gt;ṉāyiṉaḷ piṟavu māyiṭaip pirivē.&lt;/l&gt;&lt;/lg&gt;
