&lt;l&gt;pulaimaka ṉātaliṟ poynniṉ vāymoḻi&lt;/l&gt;
&lt;l&gt;nilla&lt;del rend="scribble"&gt;&lt;gap reason="illegible" unit="character" quantity="1"/&gt;&lt;/del&gt;ṟ pāṇa &lt;g rend="vowel-sign"&gt;e&lt;/g&gt;&lt;gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="3"/&gt;&lt;lb n="8"/&gt;&lt;gap reason="lost" unit="character" quantity="1"/&gt;p paraya&lt;/l&gt;
&lt;l&gt;pakaleñ cērik kāṇi&lt;/l&gt;
&lt;l&gt;ṉakalvaya lūra &lt;del rend="scribble"&gt;ṉa&lt;/del&gt;ṉāṇavum peṟumē.&lt;/l&gt;&lt;/lg&gt;
&lt;p xml:id="TNV25koḷu1"&gt; pāṇaṉukku vāyiṉ maṟuttatu. &lt;/p&gt;
